#: src/view/09_component_children.md:176
msgid "Manipulating Children"
msgstr ""

#: src/view/09_component_children.md:178
msgid ""
"The [`Fragment`](https://docs.rs/leptos/latest/leptos/tachys/view/fragment/"
"struct.Fragment.html) type is basically a way of wrapping a `Vec<AnyView>`. "
"You can insert it anywhere into your view."
msgstr ""

#: src/view/09_component_children.md:181
msgid ""
"But you can also access those inner views directly to manipulate them. For "
"example, here’s a component that takes its children and turns them into an "
"unordered list."
msgstr ""

